# Pyi-thon ships as a client-side app.
# Do not place provider secrets in Vite env vars for public builds:
# anything prefixed with VITE_ is embedded into the browser bundle.
#
# Recommended approaches:
# 1. Keep this file empty for static deployments.
# 2. Enter your own API key in the in-app Settings panel at runtime.
# 3. If you need shared credentials, call the AI provider from a server-side proxy instead.
